OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FHeat pump grant rules to be
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Frelaxed                    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The government is relaxing rules on    
OL,6, insulation to make it easier for       
OL,7, householders to qualify for a #7,500   
OL,8, heat pump grant, it has said.          
OL,10,FCavity wall and loft insulation will no
OL,11,Flonger be mandatory, it said.          
OL,13,FIt is also delaying bringing in fines  
OL,14,Ffor boiler manufacturers who do not hit
OL,15,Fheat pump sales targets.               
OL,17,FBoiler manufacturers have been pushing 
OL,18,Fup the price of gas boilers by up to   
OL,19,F#120 which they have said is in        
OL,20,Fanticipation of the fines.             
